  "snippet": "Jouw Inschrijving bij Eneco is bijna voltooid! Beste Denys, Zonet begon je aan het inschrijvingsformulier om klant te worden bij Eneco en mee te stappen in ons verhaal van Belgische en duurzame energie",
  "subject": "Jouw inschrijving bij Eneco is bijna voltooid!",
  "from": "Eneco klantendienst <welcome@eneco.be>",
  "date": "Fri, 06 Mar 2026 15:44:51 +0000 (UTC)",
  "body": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\r\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\r\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\" />\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width; initial-scale=1.0; maximum-scale=1.0; user-scalable=no;\" />\r\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=9; IE=8; IE=7; IE=EDGE\" />\r\n    <title>Jouw inschrijving bij Eneco is bijna voltooid!</title>\r\n    <style type=\"text/css\">\r\n        /* Some resets and issue fixes */\r\n        #outlook a {\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        body {\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\r\n            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\r\n            margin: 0;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .ReadMsgBody {\r\n            width: 100%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .ExternalClass {\r\n            width: 100%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .backgroundTable {\r\n            margin: 0 auto;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .table-wrapper {\r\n            margin: 0;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n            line-height: 100% !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        table {\r\n            border-collapse: collapse;\r\n            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;\r\n            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n            table td {\r\n                border-collapse: collapse;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        .ExternalClass * {\r\n            line-height: 115%;\r\n        }\r\n        /* End reset */\r\n        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {\r\n            .table-full {\r\n                width: 100% !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .td-padding-outer {\r\n                padding-left: 0px !important;\r\n                padding-right: 0px !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .td-padding-inner {\r\n                padding-left: 25px !important;\r\n                padding-right: 25px !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .td-hide {\r\n                display: none !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .td-title {\r\n                font-size: 30px !important;\r\n                line-height: 36px !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .img-full {\r\n                width: 100% !important;\r\n                height: auto !important;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body style=\"padding:0; margin:0; background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n\r\n    <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin:0; padding:0;\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                <!-- TITLE -->\r\n                <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\">\r\n                            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\">\r\n                                <tr>\r\n                                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:15px 0 20px 0;\">\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-title\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:40px; line-height:46px; color:#09354B; font-weight:bold;\">Jouw Inschrijving bij Eneco is bijna voltooid!</td>\r\n                                            </tr>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n                                    </td>\r\n                                </tr>\r\n                            </table>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </table>\r\n                <!-- TITLE -->\r\n                <!-- CLIENT NR -->\r\n                <!--<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\" style=\"{CustomerIdStyle}\">\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\">\r\n                            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" style=\"{CustomerIdStyle}\">\r\n                                <tr>\r\n                                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:15px 40px 10px 0;\">\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"{CustomerIdStyle}\">\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:12px; line-height:18px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold;\">Klant n&deg;: {CustomerId}</td>\r\n                                            </tr>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n                                    </td>\r\n                                </tr>\r\n                            </table>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </table>-->\r\n                <!-- CLIENT NR -->\r\n                <!-- INTRO -->\r\n                <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\">\r\n                            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">\r\n                                <tr>\r\n                                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:10px 40px;\">\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#000000; padding-bottom:20px;\">\r\n                                                    Beste Denys,<br />\r\n                                                    <br />Zonet begon je aan het inschrijvingsformulier om klant te worden bij Eneco en mee te stappen in ons verhaal van Belgische en duurzame energie. We hebben gemerkt dat je het formulier niet volledig kon invullen.\r\n                                                    <br /><br />\r\n                                                    Gelukkig hielden wij al jouw gegevens nog even bij en kun je jouw inschrijving eenvoudig voltooien.\r\n                                                </td>\r\n                                            </tr>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n                                    </td>\r\n                                </tr>\r\n                            </table>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </table>\r\n                <!-- INTRO -->\r\n                <!-- CTA -->\r\n                <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\">\r\n                            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\">\r\n                                <tr>\r\n                                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:20px 0 20px 0;\">\r\n                                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n                                            <tr>\r\n                                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                                                    <table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                                                        <tr>\r\n                                                            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" bgcolor=\"#EA754F\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:18px; line-height:24px; color:#FFFFFF; padding:10px 30px; border-radius:5px;\">\r\n                                                                <a href=\"https://my.eneco.be/nl/Shop/LostOlr/X4q_KbH6GkC3YOyp4M2erA/EFF?ns_campaign=permanent&amp;ns_source=lost_nl&amp;ns_mchannel=email&amp;ns_linkname=na&amp;ns_fee=0?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=lostolrmail&amp;utm_campaign=lostolr\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF; text-decoration:none;\">Inschrijving voltooien</a>\r\n                                                            </td>\r\n                                                        </tr>\r\n                                                    </table>\r\n                                                </td>\r\n                                            </tr>\r\n                                        </table>\r\n                                    </td>\r\n                                </tr>\r\n                            </table>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </table>\r\n                <!-- CTA -->\r\n                <!-- HELP -->\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\">\r\n            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:20px 40px 50px 40px;\">\r\n                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:24px; line-height:30px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; padding-bottom:10px;\">We zijn er voor jou</td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#000000;\">\r\n                                    Heb je nog vragen? Bel gerust iedere werkdag tussen 8 en 18 uur naar <strong>015 68 68 58</strong> of surf naar ons\r\n                                    <a href=\"https://eneco.be/nl/formulieren/contact/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=lostolrmail&utm_campaign=lostolr\" style=\"color:#D21242; text-decoration:underline;\">contactformulier</a>.\r\n                                    <br /><br />Met vriendelijke groeten,<br />\r\n                                    <strong>Het Eneco-team</strong>\r\n                                </td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- HELP -->\r\n<!-- CONTACT -->\r\n<table width=\"33%\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#F3F3F3\">\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\" style=\"padding:20px 0 20px 0;\">\r\n            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\" bgcolor=\"#F3F3F3\">\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                                    <table width=\"100%\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\">\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:22px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://my.eneco.be/nl/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=lostolrmail&utm_campaign=lostolr\" style=\"color:#000000; text-decoration:none;\">> My Eneco</a></td>\r\n                                            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:22px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://eneco.be/nl/contact?utm_medium=email&utm_source=lostolrmail&utm_campaign=lostolr\" style=\"color:#000000; text-decoration:none;\">> Veelgestelde vragen</a></td>\r\n                                            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:22px; color:#000000; font-weight:bold; text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://eneco.be/nl/contact?utm_medium=email&utm_source=lostolrmail&utm_campaign=lostolr\" style=\"color:#000000; text-decoration:none;\">> Klantendienst</a></td>\r\n                                        </tr>\r\n                                    </table>\r\n                                </td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- CONTACT -->\r\n<!-- FOOTER -->\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-outer\" style=\"padding:20px 0 20px 0;\">\r\n            <table width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-full\">\r\n                <tr>\r\n                    <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" class=\"td-padding-inner\" style=\"padding:0 40px;\">\r\n                        <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n                            <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:10px; line-height:16px; color:#7F7F7F;\">Eneco Belgium nv – Battelsesteenweg 455i – 2800 Mechelen – btw BE 0683.948.879<br />&copy; Eneco \r\n                                    - <a href=\"https://my.eneco.be/nl/Optin/EditOptin?utm_medium=email&utm_source=lostolrmail&utm_campaign=lostolr\" style=\"color:#626262; text-decoration:underline;\">Bepaal zelf hoeveel en waarover je van ons wil horen. Power to the people!</a>\r\n                                    – <a href=\"https://uat.eneco.be/nl/privacybeleid?utm_medium=email&utm_source=lostolrmail&utm_campaign=lostolr\" style=\"color:#7F7F7F; text-decoration:underline;\">Privacybeleid</a></td>\r\n                            </tr>\r\n                        </table>\r\n                    </td>\r\n                </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n        </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- FOOTER -->\r\n<!-- START GMAIL FIX -->\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"table-wrapper\">\r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top